room_title: Escape room "PROstate Farm" by Solve Who, LLC in San Diego
room_description: An office scoffs while the boss is permanently laid off... Search the crime scene for clues to William Lumbergh’s brutal murder at his own insurance agency: PROstate Farm. Police have brought in 3 suspects for questioning and it’s up to you to decide which of the 3 committed the murder. Relate the clues and forensic evidence you’ve found to each suspect’s testimony, and collectively decide who killed the bad boss... Solve Who!
